Expectation, and, to raise Pity in him,
she shed Tears very plentifully, and
cry'd she was a poor Widow, who
had lately lost her Husband, and
therefore hop'd he would have some
Compassion on her.$] (^D--n me, you B--ch^) ,
[$quoth (^Old-Mobb^) ) $] (^and your Husband too; 
