and the end of her Tears begins in another
Husband^) . Indeed [$ (said the 
Gentlewoman) $] my late Husband was so very
good to me, that I shall never think
<P 21>
of Marrying another, because I shall
not find the like of him again, for
Kindness. [$Quoth (^Old-Mobb^) then,$] (^Hold
