there were some Highway-men before,
wherefore he advis'd him, if he had
any Charge about him, to turn back.
Quoth (^Holloway^) ,$] (^I have no great Charge
about me, Sir, however I'll take your
Advice for fear of the worst^) . [$So as they
<P 100>
